{"tid":2259524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美上訴法院駁回華府有關立即實施WeChat禁令要求","createTime":"2020-10-27T01:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T04:30:35.000Z","uid":295230,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"05130bffdb27eaea5dc33cdcef1b98453b407cba","tid":2259524,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"美國上訴法院駁回特朗普政府有關立即實施WeChat禁令的要求。<br />\n<br />\n由3名法官組成的第九巡迴上訴法院，駁回美國司法部要求立即將騰訊旗下即時通訊軟件WeChat，在蘋果和Google的美國應用程式商店下架的上訴。裁決指，美國政府未有證明暫緩執行WeChat禁令，會立即遭受無法挽回的損害。<br />\n<br />\n三藩市法官上周五拒絕了司法部立即實施WeChat禁令的要求，司法部就裁決上訴至第九巡迴上訴法院。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府早前發出行政命令，以威脅國家安全為理由，要求蘋果和Google在美國的應用程式商店將WeChat下架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備上最高法院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe9e89fd4a8e1cefeabb9a913f462dfac83dfaf","tid":2259524,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=410566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410566&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f274dbea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410566&h=a14acb1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=410566</a>"},{"pid":"68719f6391453c366d519767c9ab65270404c5d5","tid":2259524,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:54:39.000Z","msg":"中美友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caff96243a79f88167fb2847a7a1aba5859a4dcc","tid":2259524,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de79031ed252b2b409493df0a8783938ae66f985","tid